e, but also into questions that trouble us to this day and into questions of political life more generally.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aPolitical science. 4aPhilosophy : History of Philosophy. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Philosophy. 4aPolitics and Law : Political Theory. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / History & Theory.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978143842794240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438427942423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438427942/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles